These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different nationalities: egyptian, dutch
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: surfing, cricket
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, van
1. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
2. the dutch is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| Nationality   | dutch    | egyptian |
| Sport         | cricket | surfing    |
| Transport     | motorbike     | van      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, water
There are 2 different nationalities: australian, japanese
The people use 2 different means of transport: trike, scooter
1. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the australian is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |
| Beverage      | water  | hot-chocolate   |
| Nationality   | japanese | australian  |
| Transport     | scooter   | trike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: filmmaking, sudoku
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: adventure, disaster
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: badminton, soccer
1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is in an even position##4
2. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |
| Hobby         | filmmaking   | sudoku  |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | adventure  |
| Sport         | badminton   | soccer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-4::.
There 2 different types of food: banana, garlic
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: musical, sports
The people use 2 different means of transport: quad-bike, helicopter
1. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
2. the person eating banana is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |
| Food          | banana | garlic |
| Movie-Genre   | sports   | musical   |
| Transport     | helicopter       | quad-bike      |

