.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-7::.
There 2 different types of food: tomato, cauliflower
The people have 2 different jobs:  teacher, project-manager
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: basketball, badminton
1. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the teacher##1
2. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left or right of the person who's sport is badminton##3
3. the person eating tomato is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Food    | cauliflower | tomato     |
| Job     | project-manager | teacher |
| Sport   | badminton | basketball    |

 #################################

 
