.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-14::.
There 2 different types of food: grapefruit, tomato
The people have 2 different hobbies: puzzles, fishing
2 different pets are kept: frog, turtle
1. the owner of the turtle is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person eating grapefruit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |
| Food    | tomato | grapefruit  |
| Hobby   | fishing | puzzles |
| Pet     | frog  | turtle     |

