.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-15::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: fishing, singing
There are 2 different nationalities: australian, dutch
2 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, dog
1. the owner of the dog is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
2. the australian is on the left of the dutch##1
3. the person who's hobby is fishing is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |
| Hobby         | singing | fishing |
| Nationality   | australian     | dutch     |
| Pet           | dog          | guinea-pig     |

 #################################

 
